  "texts": [
    "The challenge lies in distinguishing AI-assisted writing from entirely original human composition, a task made more difficult by the sophistication of AI in mimicking human writing styles.",
    "To address this evolving landscape, educational institutions must develop new frameworks that acknowledge the role of AI in academic writing while preserving the core values of academic integrity.",
    "This includes creating guidelines for the ethical use of AI in research and writing and equipping both students and educators with the necessary skills and knowledge to navigate this new terrain.",
    "The goal should be to leverage AI as a tool for enhancing the educational experience, rather than as a means to replace the critical thinking and creative processes that are central to learning.",
    "By doing so, educators can bridge the AI-literacy gap and foster an environment where technology augments, rather than undermines, the pursuit of knowledge."
  ],
